textAfterTable: No other products/lot numbers are affected by this recall. These products were distributed through select retailers, distributors and on-line consumer purchases in 29 states including California. There have been no reports of illness related to this product to date. Consumers should immediately discontinue use of any affected product and should dispose of them in ways that people and animals, including wild animals, cannot access them, such as placing them in a securely lidded garbage can. For more information on the recall, consumers can contact the customer service line for Pro-Pet at 1-888-765-4190.
